{
  "texts": [
    "When combined with appropriate prompt engineering strategies, the accuracy level achieves over 0.8 in extracting information related to study design, sample size, data source, patient, comparison and outcomes.",
    "Moreover, the improvement in efficiency is remarkable by reducing 8 to 10 hours of human labor to under 5 minutes (GPT-3.5) or 40 minutes (GPT-4.0).",
    "Our research pioneers the exploration of a new generation of Large Language Models in medical evidence summarization and offers potential applications in various scenarios.",
    "It provides empirical evidence to support the development of credible automatic tools for medical literature screening and review.",
    "With critical information extracted, automatic tools can strike a balance between efficiency and transparency.The field of large language models is rapidly advancing."
  ]
}